{"an4.47:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.47 ","an4.47:0.2":"5. Rohitassavagga ","an4.47:0.3":"Suvidurasutta ","an4.47:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, suviduravidurani. ","an4.47:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.47:1.3":"Nabhanca, bhikkhave, pathavi ca; ","an4.47:1.4":"idam pathamam suviduravidure. ","an4.47:1.5":"Orimanca, bhikkhave, tiram samuddassa parimanca; ","an4.47:1.6":"idam dutiyam suviduravidure. ","an4.47:1.7":"Yato ca, bhikkhave, verocano abbhudeti yattha ca atthameti; ","an4.47:1.8":"idam tatiyam suviduravidure. ","an4.47:1.9":"Satanca, bhikkhave, dhammo asatanca dhammo; ","an4.47:1.10":"idam catuttham suviduravidure. ","an4.47:1.11":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari suviduraviduraniti. ","an4.47:2.1":"Nabhanca dure pathavi ca dure, ","an4.47:2.2":"Param samuddassa tadahu dure; ","an4.47:2.3":"Yato ca verocano abbhudeti, ","an4.47:2.4":"Pabhankaro yattha ca atthameti; ","an4.47:2.5":"Tato have durataram vadanti, ","an4.47:2.6":"Satanca dhammam asatanca dhammam. ","an4.47:3.1":"Abyayiko hoti satam samagamo, ","an4.47:3.2":"Yavapi tittheyya tatheva hoti; ","an4.47:3.3":"Khippanhi veti asatam samagamo, ","an4.47:3.4":"Tasma satam dhammo asabbhi araka”ti. ","an4.47:3.5":"Sattamam. "}